Lexmark Forms Composer is a forms design tool for use with Lexmark electronic forms solutions. The tool enables the creative forms professional to design PDF based formsets for use with electronic forms solutions including Lexmark Document Producer, Lexmark Document Portal and Lexmark Forms Card. Using this tool, forms professionals can add life to existing unformatted data by creating templates to reorganize data, add graphical design elements and change font characteristics to increase the readability of the hard copy document.
